                         *********SOMBOR Presents********** 

                                   (April 2011)       


                **********Counter-Strike 1.6 and HLDS (2in1)********** 







 What's New:


 - This Counter-Strike Support only protocol 48 

 - Game engine is build 4554 

 - Included Dedicated Server (HLDS)

 - Playing on internet is faster then other versions of Counter-Strike 1.6

 - Installation is easy, small and fast

 - Works on Windows 7 (SP1), Vista (SP1, SP2) and XP (SP1, SP2, SP3) (x64 also works)

 - Included Bots in Single Player

 - Added New maps (awp_map, de_dust2_long, de_dust 2002, de_westwood, de_rats, fy_snow, 35_hp v2)

 - Steam engine is updated to latest version

 - Using css.setti server list

 - Using Rev Emulator

 - All bugs were fixed

 - Startup music is changed to: Basic Element &quot;Touch You Right Now&quot;

 - Skin is changed from green to silver color

 - Background is changed (Startup Screen)

 - All unused files in Half-Life and Counter-Strike 1.6 directory were removed (Sounds, Text files, Images etc.)

 - NOTE: - If you have problems with sound and graphics try to reinstall drivers 

